Python Installation Steps

1. Command to Install Python on Windows Machina via Powershell 

> winget install -e --id Python.Python.3.12 --scope machine

Now , check version with - python --version

2. To install Python on Ubuntu or most Linux systems, use this one-line command in your terminal:

> sudo apt update && sudo apt install python3

After installation, verify it with: python3 --version
